✅ 13) Fetch API ⭐⭐

The Fetch API is used to make HTTP requests (GET, POST, PUT, DELETE) to a server and get data.
👉 Mostly used to call APIs and work with JSON data.
📌 It returns a Promise

Fetch API Key Points (Interview Gold ⭐)
